text.section:
A person may not, in violation of this subtitle or any regulation adopted under it:
Establish or construct any new structure;
Make any new use of any existing structure or land;
Substantially alter any existing structure or use of land; or
As to any tree or other vegetation:
Plant or replant any of such a height as to be an airport hazard;
Allow any to grow to such a height as to be an airport hazard; or
Even if it is nonconforming, allow any that is an existing airport hazard to grow any higher.
